description2:
The switch is equipped with 6 ports 1000Base-T, of which 3 support 802.3af / at ( PoE, PoE + ) and 1 port supports 802.3bt ( HiPoE ).
The switch supports the function Watchdog - automatic detection of hanging equipment and reloading of PoE power at the port.
WIF-PS305G is equipped with an additional Default / operating mode switch / VLAN / Extend. Default mode — normal operation. Mode Vlan — port insulation mode; allows you to isolate the traffic of connected devices at a physical level, which limits their communication at the 2nd and 3rd levels, and guarantees the safety of content transfer. Mode Extend — PoE transmission mode up to 250 meters; allows you to overcome the barrier of 100 meters, standard for Ethernet networks, and connect remote devices without using PoE-repiters. Reliable internal silent power supply, Developed by Wi-Tek guarantees uninterrupted operation for a long service life, and its internal execution simplifies the installation and operation of equipment, as well as saves space during installation. An increased nominal budget allows you to solve most of the tasks of connecting PoE equipment.
PoE ports ( RJ45 ): PoE ports from 2 to 4 ( standard 802.3 af / at ) up to 30W on port
